{"tid":2311250,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"以炒飯嚟講，泰式炒飯應該勝過中式和日式","createTime":"2020-12-04T02:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T02:02:39.000Z","uid":38539,"like":10,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c2943a553fab7cfb1ce155c6fda3975e19ea5a","tid":2311250,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"泰式 &gt; 中式 &gt; 日式 &gt; 印尼<br />\n<br />\n泰式炒飯通常都會落啲辣味香料，加埋金不換陣香味，諗起都流口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QZrkjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QZrkjB.jpg&h=29463d5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中式楊州炒飯，蝦肉爽脆，叉燒的甜，食落好有層次感<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyECrWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyECrWA.jpg&h=7eb16c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日式炒飯，啲配料比較兒童向，我稱之為細蚊仔炒飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zh3vMW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZh3vMW2.jpg&h=3bcd2406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n印尼炒飯，三色豆炒加塊蛋咁囉，<br />\n印象中從來無食過會覺得好食的印尼炒飯，純屬個人偏見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLBAX4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLBAX4P.jpg&h=27822f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e648eee064ca44ce6ebdedc97e7657394cc812b","tid":2311250,"uid":243121,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"但泰式比較濕 我覺得炒飯要乾身 粒粒分明"},{"pid":"2c525a7e54430f025f0d6f5e5d738d45299539de","tid":2311250,"uid":331590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"唉, 比咩春"},{"pid":"a21daf7cb8623abc2ce3083a4deb604d09fdde70","tid":2311250,"uid":144014,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FOjFor.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FOjFor.jpg&h=7088162e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCM9h96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCM9h96.jpg&h=f5f8b77f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王耀霆同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d949af084cee3270def2176807b0af1f289b25","tid":2311250,"uid":262459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"印尼炒飯好正wor！但有啲炒得太鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c296aaa2d4f3c38d6b8fc99e448fea65ebf29ca","tid":2311250,"uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔理咩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落咗三色豆就是屎式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc07d7a1e1d0cc5646f00be5f1dadede63795c3","tid":2311250,"uid":140189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c296aaa2d4f3c38d6b8fc99e448fea65ebf29ca","tid":2311250,"uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔理咩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落咗三色豆就是屎式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"豆豆師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw我都係見到豆就唔開胃"},{"pid":"e1911702c9325f7bce7afe1b2141e0d0fd9cac12","tid":2311250,"uid":312524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c296aaa2d4f3c38d6b8fc99e448fea65ebf29ca","tid":2311250,"uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔理咩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落咗三色豆就是屎式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"粟米都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd豆豆同紅蘿蔔真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeafe31d3299f03b872ae5611f016e5b4c71bd6","tid":2311250,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4e648eee064ca44ce6ebdedc97e7657394cc812b","tid":2311250,"uid":243121,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"但泰式比較濕 我覺得炒飯要乾身 粒粒分明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇情況<br />\n中式炒飯主角係個飯，其他配料反而無咁重要，<br />\n而且佢啲香料無咁重，主要食個鑊氣，<br />\n所以一濕通常都係代表個飯炒得唔好，<br />\n就好似開演員會咁，個歌手走哂音，<br />\n就算樂隊彈得幾咁好都無補於事。<br />\n<br />\n但係泰式炒飯本身重口味，有辣椒、金不換呢啲重味香料，<br />\n雖然水份多飯濕，但唔會影響到碟炒飯的整體味道，<br />\n就好一隊band，每個樂手之間互相關聯，一即是全，全即是一。"},{"pid":"72ab93570d4fcff44340de500c46815c3f8ce23c","tid":2311250,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c296aaa2d4f3c38d6b8fc99e448fea65ebf29ca","tid":2311250,"uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔理咩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落咗三色豆就是屎式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"印仔偏食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bba849aa70b4ce6f11f26ac5b8288dab398a496","tid":2311250,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e1911702c9325f7bce7afe1b2141e0d0fd9cac12","tid":2311250,"uid":312524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c296aaa2d4f3c38d6b8fc99e448fea65ebf29ca","tid":2311250,"uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔理咩式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落咗三色豆就是屎式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"粟米都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd豆豆同紅蘿蔔真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"炒飯加三色豆個層次會豐富咗<img 